==English==

===Noun===
'''Sumerian'''

#A person from [[Sumeria]] or of Sumerian descent.
#A native of lower [[Babylonia]], anciently called Sumer
#The ancient language spoken in [[Sumeria]]

===Adjective===
'''Sumerian'''

#Of, from, or pertaining to Sumeria, the Sumerian people or the Sumerian language.
#Of or pertaining to the people, language, or region of lower Babylonia, which was anciently called Sumer

